{"73716":{"detail":{"date":"2000-02-06","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/09/ed/73716_fKpkQ.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/09/ed/73716_fKpkQ.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/09/ed/73716_fKpkQ.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/09/ed/73716_fKpkQ.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/09/ed/73716_fKpkQ.jpg"},"summary":"在外形古怪的山猫山上，有一座猫城。里面有一只没有猫尾巴、猫须的蒙面猫侠。只要谁有危难一喊“救命”他就会出现帮忙。在猫城人气极高。但这样就遭到南奥的嫉妒……南奥誓要取得猫城人气王的名誉。究竟南奥会怎麼做呢？蒙面猫侠的真实身份竟然是平时胆小怕事的拉高！？剧情高潮迭起又新奇又有趣。","name":"ニャニがニャンだー ニャンダーかめん","name_cn":"蒙面猫侠","tags":[{"name":"TVB","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"童年","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2000","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"搞笑","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"SUNRISE","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"蒙面猫侠","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"经典","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"子供向","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"かないみか","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TVA","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2001","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"长篇","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"サンライズ","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"浅野まゆみ","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"芝山努","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"桜井正明","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"川田妙子","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"岩崎知子","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"蒙面猫侠"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"ニャンダーかめん"}]},{"key":"话数","value":"83"},{"key":"放送开始","value":"2000年2月6日"},{"key":"其他电视台","value":"TVB"},{"key":"播放结束","value":"2001年9月30日"},{"key":"导演","value":"岩崎知子"},{"key":"音乐","value":"宮路一昭"},{"key":"制作","value":"メ～テレ、东急エージェンシー、SUNRISE"},{"key":"企画","value":"サンライズ"},{"key":"原作","value":"やなせたかし「ニャニがニャンだー ニャンダーかめん」より（講談社刊）"},{"key":"系列构成","val